    {
      "author": "Sir Simpel",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107483872308418373436?hl=id",
      "rating": 5,
      "text": "Surprisingly, food was great. Recommended food, roti bakar kaya, coffee and the noodles. Service was a little bit too slow as the waiters are few and the restaurant was busy when we came. You can park your car to the building next to the restaurant as the restaurant owner has the same building, few building away. The renovation of the restaurant is simple, nothing extraordinary. We would come back for the food maybe as there are many other menu we would like to try.",
      "textTranslated": "Yang mengejutkan, makanannya enak sekali. Makanan yang direkomendasikan adalah roti bakar kaya, kopi, dan mie. Pelayanannya agak lambat karena jumlah pelayan sedikit dan restoran sedang ramai saat kami datang. Anda bisa memarkir mobil di gedung sebelah restoran karena pemilik restoran juga memiliki gedung yang sama, hanya beberapa gedung di dekatnya. Renovasi restoran sederhana, tidak ada yang istimewa. Kami mungkin akan kembali lagi untuk makanannya karena ada banyak menu lain yang ingin kami coba.",
      "date": "2025-12-19T08:39:35.982Z",
      "relativeDate": "3 bulan lalu",
      "likesCount": 0,
      "responseFromOwner": null,
